OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFTSE 100 bosses 'earn UK   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faverage salary by lunch'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Bosses of Britain's biggest companies  
OL,6, will earn more by lunchtime than the   
OL,7, typical worker will all year, research 
OL,8, claims.                                
OL,10,FBy 13:00 GMT on Thursday, the pay of   
OL,11,FFTSE 100 chiefs will have overtaken the
OL,12,F#34,963 annual median wage for         
OL,13,Ffull-time workers, the High Pay Centre 
OL,14,Fsays.                                  
OL,16,FIncluding pensions, top bosses' average
OL,17,Freward amounts to #3.81m per year, the 
OL,18,Fcentre says.                           
OL,20,FThat works out to #1,170 per hour - 109
OL,21,Ftimes the average full-time worker.    
